{{Infobox book | name = Dating Dead Men | image = Dating Dead Men.jpg | author = [[Harley Jane Kozak]] | genre = [[Mystery fiction]], [[Humour]], [[Thriller (genre)|Thriller]] | published = 2004 | publisher = [[Doubleday (publisher)|Doubleday]] | isbn = 978-0-385-51018-9 | alt = Dating Dead Men | pages = 336 | website = {{URL|http://www.harleyjanekozak.com/datingdeadmen.php|Dating Dead Men}} | awards = [[Anthony Award|Anthony Award for Best First Novel]] (2005) }}
